<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>온 (溫) - 따뜻함을 담은 다이닝</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@300;500;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            dark: '#1a1a1a',
            gold: '#D4AF37',
            cream: '#f5f5f0',
          },
          fontFamily: {
            serif: ['Playfair Display', 'serif'],
            kr: ['Noto Serif KR', 'serif'],
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-dark text-cream font-kr font-light">

  <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 px-6 py-6 flex justify-between items-center mix-blend-difference">
    <div class="text-2xl font-serif italic text-white z-50">ON Dining</div>
    <div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 text-sm text-gray-300 z-50">
      <a href="#menu" class="hover:text-white transition">메뉴</a>
      <a href="#story" class="hover:text-white transition">이야기</a>
      <a href="#reservation" class="hover:text-white transition">예약</a>
    </div>
    <button onclick="toggleDining()" class="border border-white/30 px-6 py-2 text-xs hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition z-50">
      RESERVE
    </button>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <header class="h-screen flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Video Placeholder -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514362545857-3bc16c4c7d1b?q=80&w=1920" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 zoom-effect">
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center space-y-8 animate-fade-in-up">
      <div class="border-l border-r border-white/20 px-8 py-2 inline-block">
        <span class="text-xs tracking-[0.5em] uppercase">Korean Contemporary</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-serif italic leading-none">
        Taste of <br> <span class="text-gold not-italic font-kr font-bold">溫 (ON)</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-300 tracking-wider font-kr max-w-lg mx-auto leading-loose">
        계절의 온기를 담아낸 정성스러운 한 끼.<br>
        시간이 멈춘 듯한 공간에서 깊은 맛의 여운을 즐기세요.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-xs tracking-widest text-gold animate-bounce">
      SCROLL
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Menu Section -->
  <section id="menu" class="py-24 px-6 bg-[#161616]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl mb-4 italic text-gold">Dining Course</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">제철 식재료에 따라 구성이 변경될 수 있습니다.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Course A -->
        <div class="group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleDining()">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline border-b border-white/10 pb-4 mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif italic">Lunch Standard</h3>
            <span class="text-gold font-bold">₩ 85,000</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            아뮤즈 부쉬 • 제철 생선회 • 트러플 감자 뇨끼 • 한우 채끝 등심 (+2.0) 또는 이베리코 프렌치랙 • 셔벗 • 다과와 차
          </p>
          <div class="h-0 group-hover:h-48 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-700">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559339352-11d035aa65de?q=80&w=800" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded opacity-80">
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Course B -->
        <div class="group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleDining()">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline border-b border-white/10 pb-4 mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif italic">Dinner Signature</h3>
            <span class="text-gold font-bold">₩ 150,000</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            웰컴 디쉬 • 캐비어와 도미 • 랍스터 비스크 • 전복 리조또 • 한우 안심 스테이크 • 셰프 스페셜 디저트 • 쁘띠 푸르
          </p>
          <div class="h-0 group-hover:h-48 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-700">
             <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504674900247-0877df9cc836?q=80&w=800" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded opacity-80">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Reservation Modal -->
  <div id="dining-modal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/90 z-[60] hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="bg-[#1f1f1f] border border-white/10 w-full max-w-md p-10 relative">
      <button onclick="toggleDining()" class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-gray-500 hover:text-white">✕</button>
      
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl italic text-gold mb-2">Reservation</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 tracking-widest">소중한 분과의 시간을 준비하겠습니다</p>
      </div>

      <form class="space-y-6" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('예약 신청이 접수되었습니다. (예약금 안내 문자 발송)'); toggleDining();">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="text-xs text-gold uppercase tracking-wider">Date</label>
            <input type="date" class="w-full bg-transparent border-b border-gray-700 text-cream py-2 outline-none focus:border-gold transition text-sm">
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="text-xs text-gold uppercase tracking-wider">Guests</label>
            <select class="w-full bg-transparent border-b border-gray-700 text-cream py-2 outline-none focus:border-gold transition text-sm">
              <option class="bg-dark">2 People</option>
              <option class="bg-dark">3 People</option>
              <option class="bg-dark">4 People</option>
              <option class="bg-dark">5+ (Room)</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2">
           <label class="text-xs text-gold uppercase tracking-wider">Name</label>
           <input type="text" class="w-full bg-transparent border-b border-gray-700 text-cream py-2 outline-none focus:border-gold transition">
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2">
           <label class="text-xs text-gold uppercase tracking-wider">Contact</label>
           <input type="tel" placeholder="010-0000-0000" class="w-full bg-transparent border-b border-gray-700 text-cream py-2 outline-none focus:border-gold transition">
        </div>
        
        <button class="w-full bg-gold text-dark py-4 font-serif italic text-lg hover:bg-white transition mt-4">
          Book Table
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .zoom-effect { animation: zoom 20s infinite alternate; }
    @keyframes zoom { from { transform: scale(1); } to { transform: scale(1.1); } }
  </style>

  <script>
    function toggleDining() {
      const modal = document.getElementById('dining-modal');
      if(modal.classList.contains('hidden')) {
        modal.classList.remove('hidden');
      } else {
        modal.classList.add('hidden');
      }
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
